div.p: Author: Alejandro Araya Jiménez, Jeremy Quirós Marín, Ricardo Artavia Solano, Sebastián Acuña Pérez

Description: This project is an integrated data processing and web application stack utilizing various services and technologies. The primary goal is to build a robust infrastructure that encompasses backend data warehousing with MongoDB and PostgreSQL, an ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) scheduler, and a frontend application using Next.js, all orchestrated through Docker Compose.
